{"tid":1792152,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"我有兩張葉問4飛唔得閒睇  後晚二連有無人要","createTime":"2019-12-21T11:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T04:56:59.000Z","uid":224836,"like":64,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"78a8aa8da0ffdc2666aa9c941a29c7f2b4aadcc4","tid":1792152,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:58:06.000Z","msg":"葉問個仔學校打交被趕出校，佢自己又確診cancer<br />\n飛去美國幫仔搵學校，華人受歧視欺凌，葉問制止欺凌，得罪美軍陸戰隊軍官。李小龍美國出書、收鬼佬徙弟教功夫，引起唐人街華人武術界不滿。李小龍有美軍徒弟想將詠春引入部隊，受空手道教官打壓，派人去唐人街踢館，被葉問狠狠教訓。美國軍官同時派人打傷大量唐人街武師，搵移民局拉人。最後葉問入軍營挑機，打贏軍官。最後放棄個仔留學計劃，親自教個仔詠春。最後病發身亡。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ab3f2c57401e23ea555d51b1e7fd8f50207289","tid":1792152,"uid":311583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:58:40.000Z","msg":"【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792093</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=772efa92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0e